        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-8f22f363-121f-4283-b31e-b26ac74bc18e">
                The Prime Minister (Mr. Churchill)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-8f22f363-121f-4283-b31e-b26ac74bc18e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1944-03-09/debates/ebea7f3c-ab36-4f96-8526-f36f1f0ad88a/DelegatedDepartmentalLegislation#contribution-8f22f363-121f-4283-b31e-b26ac74bc18e">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">This matter is kept under constant review by Departments, and it is their duty to secure the repeal of any subordinate legislation which is obsolete or redundant. No special action is called for on my part.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-8f22f363-121f-4283-b31e-b26ac74bc18e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
